  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink269-kilavi">kuṟainayappak kūṟit talaimakaḷaik kūṭṭiya tōḻi yavaṉ iṭaiyiṭṭu vantu ciṟaippuṟattu niṉṟuḻit talaimakaṭkuc colluvāḷāyc colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante said, speaking as to the heroine, when the hero, having come after a gap, stood behind the hedge; the confidante who, speaking so that the heroine would grant the request, brought her [to the tryst].
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink269">
<l>kēḻa luḻuteṉak kiḷarnta veruvai</l>
<l>viḷainta ceṟuviṟ ṟōṉṟu nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>vārā tavaṇuṟai nīṭi ṉērvaḷai</l>
<l>yiṇaiyī rōti nīyaḻat</l>
<l>tuṇainaṉi yiḻakkuveṉ maṭamai yāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>If the man from the land where</l>
        <l rend="space indent">reed that has sprung up</l>
        <l rend="indent">because a boar ploughed it,</l>
        <l rend="indent">appears like a cultivated field,</l>
        <l rend="space">does not come</l>
        <l>and prolongs his stay there—</l>
        <l rend="space">as you, with fine bangles</l>
        <l>and twin wet braids, cry,</l>
        <l>I shall indeed lose</l>
        <l>your companionship</l>
        <l>through my folly.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
